				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">This is one of the most frustrating aspects of the game for almost any high level mage, be you raider, more "casual" group-based player or even soloer.
<br />

<br />
I'm trying ot figure out why this is. The effects certainly don't stack, and it seems to me that if there's an annoying, pointlessly frustrating facet of the game that needs to be adressed its right here.
<br />

<br />
Can anyone shed any light on why the LORE tag neds to be applied to these?<br />_________________<br /><A HREF="http://pub44.ezboard.com/fsilverangel89587frm56">Inspiration</A></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
